data.description: Welcome to this picturesque three-bedroom, two-bathroom pool home nestled in beautiful Inverness, Florida. Situated on the  Lakeside golf course, this property offers a truly tranquil living experience. With a living area spanning 2,588 square feet, this spacious home provides ample room for comfortable living and entertaining. The layout features three bedrooms, offering privacy and relaxation for family members and guests alike. The master bedroom is a generous retreat, complete with  his/closets, walk in shower and jacuzzi tub. Step into the heart of the home, where you'll find the kitchen, breakfast nook, dining, living and very spacious family room.  We also have a separate office if you work from home!  Beyond the living area, you'll discover a sparkling pool, perfect for cooling off on hot summer days or hosting memorable poolside gatherings. The backyard overlooks the tranquil Lakeside golf course, offering breathtaking views and a sense of tranquility. This property also boasts a three-car garage, providing plenty of space to accommodate vehicles, storage, and hobbies. The roof was recently replaced in 2021, ensuring peace of mind and protection from the elements. Additionally, the air conditioning unit was upgraded in 2018, providing reliable cooling and energy efficiency. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty of Inverness with the Withlacoochee State 46 mile bike trail just minutes away and enjoy the many Tsala Apopka chain of lakes for boating. Whether it's enjoying a round of golf, exploring nearby biking/walking trails, or simply unwinding in the peacefulness of your own backyard, this property offers an exceptional lifestyle.
